{"id":"treasure-houses","term":"Treasure houses","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The houses or magazines built for the safe keeping of treasure and valuable articles of any kind (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 5:17\">Ezra 5:17</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 7:20\">7:20</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 10:38\">Neh. 10:38</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Daniel 1:2\">Dan. 1:2</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Ezra 5:17","Ezra 7:20","Nehemiah 10:38","Daniel 1:2"]}